x4freetext: 106Cd (250 ug/cm2 thick) onto
thin carbon foils (~20 ug/cm2).
Two pairs of Si detectors mounted on two
independently rotatable turntables. Additional two Si
detectors under 15 deg for absolute normalization, to
monitor the target thickness and to take into account
the beam position on the target.
